==Works==
===Poetry===
* &quot;Serres chaudes&quot; (1889)
* &quot;Douze chansons&quot; (1896)
* &quot;Quinze chansons&quot; (expanded version of &quot;Douze chansons&quot;) (1900)

===Drama===
