* &quot;The Tidal Wave&quot;, a 1920 British silent film
* &quot;Tidal Wave&quot; (1973 film), a film based on novel &quot;Japan Sinks&quot;
* &quot;Tidal Wave&quot; (2009 film), a South Korean disaster movie

